                        "text": "pov: you finally visit the Japanese town that inspired Spirited Away.\n\nWelcome to Ginzan Onsen - a tiny hot spring town in Yamagata where wooden ryokans line a flowing river, lantern-lit streets glow at dusk, and falling snow makes you question whether you\u2019ve stepped into a film set. \n\nIt\u2019s beautiful all year but in winter, it becomes one of the most atmospheric destinations in Japan \u2744\ufe0f"
                    }
                }
